Writing Basic CloudFormation Templates for Networking
  1. Defining the Template Structure
    AWSTemplateFormatVersion: '2010-09-09'
    Description: Basic VPC Setup
    Resources:
    # VPC, Subnets, and other components go here
  2. Creating a Virtual Private Cloud (VPC)
    MyVPC:
      Type: AWS::EC2::VPC
      Properties:
        CidrBlock: 10.0.0.0/16
        EnableDnsSupport: true
        EnableDnsHostnames: true
        Tags:
          - Key: Name
            Value: MyBasicVPC
  3. Adding Public and Private Subnets
    PublicSubnet1:
      Type: AWS::EC2::Subnet
      Properties:
        VpcId: !Ref MyVPC
        CidrBlock: 10.0.1.0/24
        AvailabilityZone: !Select [ 0, !GetAZs '' ]
        MapPublicIpOnLaunch: true
        Tags:
          - Key: Name
            Value: PublicSubnet1
    PrivateSubnet1:
      Type: AWS::EC2::Subnet
      Properties:
        VpcId: !Ref MyVPC
        CidrBlock: 10.0.2.0/24
        AvailabilityZone: !Select [ 0, !GetAZs '' ]
        Tags:
          - Key: Name
            Value: PrivateSubnet1
  4. Configuring an Internet Gateway and Route Tables
    InternetGateway:
      Type: AWS::EC2::InternetGateway
      Properties:
        Tags:
          - Key: Name
            Value: MyInternetGateway
    AttachGateway:
      Type: AWS::EC2::VPCGatewayAttachment
      Properties:
        VpcId: !Ref MyVPC
        InternetGatewayId: !Ref InternetGateway
    PublicRouteTable:
      Type: AWS::EC2::RouteTable
      Properties:
        VpcId: !Ref MyVPC
    PublicRoute:
      Type: AWS::EC2::Route
      DependsOn: AttachGateway
      Properties:
        RouteTableId: !Ref PublicRouteTable
        DestinationCidrBlock: 0.0.0.0/0
        GatewayId: !Ref InternetGateway
    RouteTableAssociation:
      Type: AWS::EC2::SubnetRouteTableAssociation
      Properties:
        SubnetId: !Ref PublicSubnet1
        RouteTableId: !Ref PublicRouteTable
  5. Validating and Deploying the Template
    aws cloudformation validate-template --template-body file://template.yaml
  Once validated, you can deploy the template with:
    aws cloudformation create-stack --stack-name MyNetworkStack --template-body file://template.yaml --capabilities CAPABILITY_NAMED_IAM
  
